- Disable the checking of the InResponseToField as suggested at [ch.13 docs.spring.io/spring-security-saml][3] and for [this][4] and [this question][5].
- Configure the defaultTargetUrl of the successRedirectHandler (where I am using a custom superclass of org.springframework.security.web.authentication.SimpleUrlAuthenticationSuccessHandler) as suggested  for [this question][6]. In addition this solution is not multitenant.

```xml
&lt;bean id=&quot;successRedirectHandler&quot; class=&quot;org.MySamlAuthenticationSuccessHandler&quot; 
      						init-method=&quot;afterPropertiesSet&quot;&gt;
    &lt;property name=&quot;contextPath&quot; value=&quot;/myapi&quot; /&gt;
